title: Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw
plot: Lawman Luke Hobbs (Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson) and outcast Deckard Shaw (Jason Statham) form an unlikely alliance when a cyber-genetically enhanced villain threatens the future of humanity.
writers: Chris Morgan, Drew Pearce, Gary Scott Thompson
stars: Dwayne Johnson, Jason Statham, Idris Elba, Vanessa Kirby
companies: Chris Morgan Productions, Dentsu, Seven Bucks Productions

tagline: Saving the world is easy, but working together is going to be a real pain in the ass.
keywords: samoa,flamethrower,spin off,shared universe,fast and furious franchise

similars.title: The Fate of the Furious
similars.plot: When a mysterious woman seduces Dominic Toretto into the world of terrorism and a betrayal of those closest to him, the crew face trials that will test them as never before.
similars.stars: Vin Diesel, Jason Statham, Dwayne Johnson

similars.title: Furious 7
similars.plot: Deckard Shaw seeks revenge against Dominic Toretto and his family for his comatose brother.
similars.stars: Vin Diesel, Paul Walker, Dwayne Johnson

similars.title: Fast & Furious 6
similars.plot: Hobbs has Dominic and Brian reassemble their crew to take down a team of mercenaries: Dominic unexpectedly gets sidetracked with facing his presumed deceased girlfriend, Letty.
similars.stars: Vin Diesel, Paul Walker, Dwayne Johnson

similars.title: Fast Five
similars.plot: Dominic Toretto and his crew of street racers plan a massive heist to buy their freedom while in the sights of a powerful Brazilian drug lord and a dangerous federal agent.
similars.stars: Vin Diesel, Paul Walker, Dwayne Johnson

similars.title: The Fast and the Furious
similars.plot: Los Angeles police officer Brian O'Conner must decide where his loyalty really lies when he becomes enamored with the street racing world he has been sent undercover to destroy.
similars.stars: Vin Diesel, Paul Walker, Michelle Rodriguez

similars.title: Fast & Furious
similars.plot: Brian O'Conner, back working for the FBI in Los Angeles, teams up with Dominic Toretto to bring down a heroin importer by infiltrating his operation.
similars.stars: Vin Diesel, Paul Walker, Michelle Rodriguez

similars.title: The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift
similars.fullTitle: The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift (2006)
similars.plot: A teenager becomes a major competitor in the world of drift racing after moving in with his father in Tokyo to avoid a jail sentence in America.
similars.stars: Lucas Black, Zachery Ty Bryan, Shad Moss

similars.title: 2 Fast 2 Furious
similars.plot: Former cop Brian O'Conner is called upon to bust a dangerous criminal and he recruits the help of a former childhood friend and street racer who has a chance to redeem himself.
similars.stars: Paul Walker, Tyrese Gibson, Cole Hauser

similars.title: Jumanji: The Next Level
similars.plot: In Jumanji: The Next Level, the gang is back but the game has changed. As they return to rescue one of their own, the players will have to brave parts unknown from arid deserts to snowy mountains, to escape the world's most dangerous game.
similars.stars: Dwayne Johnson, Jack Black, Kevin Hart

similars.title: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
similars.plot: Four teenagers are sucked into a magical video game, and the only way they can escape is to work together to finish the game.
similars.stars: Dwayne Johnson, Karen Gillan, Kevin Hart

similars.title: Central Intelligence
similars.plot: After he reconnects with an awkward pal from high school through Facebook, a mild-mannered accountant is lured into the world of international espionage.
similars.stars: Dwayne Johnson, Kevin Hart, Danielle Nicolet

similars.title: Rampage
similars.plot: When three different animals become infected with a dangerous pathogen, a primatologist and a geneticist team up to stop them from destroying Chicago.
similars.stars: Dwayne Johnson, Naomie Harris, Malin Akerman
